taxi.model

Class TaxiDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • taxi.model.TaxiDriver

  • @Entity
public class TaxiDriver
extends java.lang.Object
    The Customer TaxiDriver implements all taxi drivers using the taxi service.

    Every taxi driver has only one taxi. It also has:

    • name,
    • surname,
    • sex,
    • username,
    • password,
    • dateOfBirth,
    • locationLat,
    • locationLon,
    • address,
    • city,
    • zipCode,
    • email,
    • creditCardType,
    • creditCardNumber,
    • expiryDate,
    • ccv
    Since:
    Academic Year 2016-2017
    Author:
    Team 4
